tika.dc.description:
Do you prefer classic cookies like chocolate chip, peanut butter, and oatmeal, or are you looking for something more unique, such as Cornmeal Aniseed Crescents, Sesame Logs, or Palmiers? This pocket-size cookbook even includes favorite bar cookies like biscotti, brownies, and lemon bars. No matter what you prefer to put in your cookie jar, the handy little Totally Cookies Cookbook has plenty of cookie recipes to satisfy your sweet tooth.

From the Trade Paperback edition.
